Steps for Release
=================

*) Ensure all changes are done, see git status
*) Update ChangeLog
*) Bump version in CMakeLists.txt
*) Do clean compiles in Release and Debug mode
*) Tag in git
*) Create tar.gz
*) Update .lsm
*) Upload to ftp://ktown.kde.org/incoming/stable/KDE4.x/
*) Open a bug on BKO to make the upload
*) Announce on kde-announce-apps
*) Announce in other places
